{"tid":1134191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【五一假期】內地旅行團聚集土瓜灣紅磡購物用餐","createTime":"2019-05-01T15:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:37:00.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a05824f3becb1af41389003c22179da37b9ef56","tid":1134191,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"不少內地旅行團，繼續聚集在土瓜灣和紅磡用餐和購物。<br />\n<br />\n在土瓜灣一間食肆外面，一班旅行團團友站在行人路等候進入餐廳吃飯，旁邊的馬路就泊滿旅遊巴。<br />\n<br />\n有內地遊客表示，藉五一黃金周假期到香港旅遊觀光，預計消費逾萬元。<br />\n<br />\n但有區內居民則指，大批遊客到土瓜灣購物，影響日常生活，期望商戶可協助維持秩序，控制人流。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=346432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346432&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=d12ee285\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346432&h=0d64cc67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=346432</a>"}]}